Appendix 2 - House price prediction from 0.5 million record data set

Step 1 : Collecting Data

The data set is collected in CSV format from kaggele and below is the reference for the same.

A.Sleem.(2018)Housepricing.[Online]. Available:https://www.kaggle.com/greenwing1985/housepricing

Step 2 : Exploring, preprocessing and cleaning the data
